-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"WIcHBVPlvS\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/06/26/wordpress-5-5-better-fine-grained-control-of-redirect_guess_404_permalink/\">WordPress 5.5: Better fine grained control of redirect_guess_404_permalink()</a></blockquote><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" title=\"&#8220;WordPress 5.5: Better fine grained control of redirect_guess_404_permalink()&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/06/26/wordpress-5-5-better-fine-grained-control-of-redirect_guess_404_permalink/embed/#?secret=WIcHBVPlvS\" data-secret=\"WIcHBVPlvS\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"vyzUmEVDIk\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/10/new-css-styles-for-buttons-with-disabled-state-in-wp-5-5/\">New CSS styles for buttons with disabled state in WP 5.5</a></blockquote><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" title=\"&#8220;New CSS styles for buttons with disabled state in WP 5.5&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/10/new-css-styles-for-buttons-with-disabled-state-in-wp-5-5/embed/#?secret=vyzUmEVDIk\" data-secret=\"vyzUmEVDIk\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"SknizKJZ2e\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/15/dashicons-in-wordpress-5-5-the-final-update/\">Dashicons in WordPress 5.5 (the final update)</a></blockquote><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" title=\"&#8220;Dashicons in WordPress 5.5 (the final update)&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/15/dashicons-in-wordpress-5-5-the-final-update/embed/#?secret=SknizKJZ2e\" data-secret=\"SknizKJZ2e\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"hXuSi5pXMM\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/14/php-related-improvements-changes-wordpress-5-5-edition/\">PHP related improvements &amp; changes: WordPress 5.5 edition</a></blockquote><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" title=\"&#8220;PHP related improvements &amp; changes: WordPress 5.5 edition&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/14/php-related-improvements-changes-wordpress-5-5-edition/embed/#?secret=hXuSi5pXMM\" data-secret=\"hXuSi5pXMM\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Et pour finir, un petit floril√®ge de modifications diverses et vari√©es</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cela fait en tout <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;type=defect+(bug)&amp;milestone=5.5&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=type&amp;col=owner&amp;col=priority&amp;col=component&amp;col=version&amp;order=priority\">306 correctifs</a>, <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;type=enhancement&amp;milestone=5.5&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=type&amp;col=owner&amp;col=priority&amp;col=component&amp;col=version&amp;order=priority\">157 am√©liorations et nouvelles fonctionnalit√©s</a> et <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;type=task+(blessed)&amp;milestone=5.4&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=type&amp;col=owner&amp;col=priority&amp;col=component&amp;col=version&amp;order=priority\">12 t√¢ches de gestion courante</a> qui ont √©t√© marqu√©s <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;milestone=5.5&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=owner&amp;col=type&amp;col=priority&amp;col=component&amp;col=version&amp;order=priority\">comme √©tant cl√¥tur√©s</a> dans le jalon <code>5.5</code> de WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nous souhaitons √©galement mettre en √©vidence quelques changements qui n&rsquo;ont pas fait l&rsquo;objet de notes de d√©veloppement sp√©cifiques (cliquer sur le num√©ro de ticket pour acc√©der au ticket en question sur Trac)&nbsp;:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Commentaires¬†: le calcul des nombres de commentaires et de la pagination a √©t√© corrig√© pour les commentaires non approuv√©s ‚Äì <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/8973\">#8973</a></li><li>Commentaires¬†: <code>get_comment_count()</code> retourne maintenant toujours un entier num√©rique, quelque soit l‚Äô√©tat du commentaire ‚Äì <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/48093\">#48093</a></li><li>Outil de personnalisation (customizer)¬†: l&rsquo;interface de l&rsquo;outil de personnalisation s&rsquo;adapte maintenant en fonction des couleurs alternatives √©ventuellement choisies pour l&rsquo;interface d&rsquo;administration ‚Äì <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/50547\">#50547</a></li><li>Internationalisation¬†: des crochets ont √©t√© ajout√©s pour le filtrage par <code>text-domain</code> des cha√Ænes traduisibles ‚Äì <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/49518\">#49518</a></li><li>M√©dias¬†: <code>sanitize_file_name()</code> nettoie d√©sormais correctement les noms de fichier et supprime leurs accents ‚Äì <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/22363\">#22363</a></li><li>Menus¬†: les r√©glages des menus sont maintenant directement affich√©s lors de la cr√©ation d&rsquo;un nouveau menu ‚Äì <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/44286\">#44286</a></li><li>Menus¬†: les termes de taxonomies n&rsquo;ayant aucune publication s&rsquo;affichent maintenant dans les r√©sultats de la recherche lors de l&rsquo;ajout d&rsquo;√©l√©ments dans les menus de navigation ‚Äì <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/45298\">#45298</a></li><li>Options, API WordPress.org¬†: les valeurs de m√©tadonn√©es par d√©faut sont maintenant support√©es ‚Äì <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/43941\">#43941</a></li><li>Widgets¬†: les widgets utilisant des tailles d&rsquo;images personnalis√©es affichent maintenant correctement leur l√©gende √©ventuelle ‚Äì <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/50160\">#50160</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" />\n\n\n\n<p>Pour rappel, la sortie de WordPress 5.5 est pr√©vue le 11 ao√ªt 2020. Vous pouvez d‚Äôores et d√©j√† la tester en version&nbsp;<em>Release Candidate</em>&nbsp;en installant l‚Äôextension officielle WordPress Beta Tester puis en allant dans ses r√©glages et en cochant la case&nbsp;Beta/ version de d√©veloppement puis en mettant √† jour votre installation de fa√ßon classique.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"dqGKFt2TE9\"><a href=\"https://fr.wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-beta-tester/\">WordPress Beta Tester</a></blockquote><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" title=\"¬´¬†WordPress Beta Tester¬†¬ª &#8212; Plugin Directory\" src=\"https://fr.wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-beta-tester/embed/#?secret=dqGKFt2TE9\" data-secret=\"dqGKFt2TE9\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" />\n\n\n\n<p>Cet article est une traduction du <em><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/30/wordpress-5-5-field-guide/\">Field Guide</a></em><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/30/wordpress-5-5-field-guide/\"> (en anglais)</a> de WordPress 5.5, r√©alis√©e par <a href=\"https://profile.wordpress.org/audrasjb\">Jb Audras</a> et relue par <a href=\"https://profile.wordpress.org/chaton666\">Marie Comet</a>, <a href=\"https://profile.wordpress.org/bastho\">Bastien Ho</a> et <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wolforg\">Wolforg</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:94:\"https://fr.wordpress.org/2020/07/31/les-changements-techniques-a-venir-sur-wordpress-5-5/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"La documentation de WordPress est maintenant disponible en fran√ßais\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:104:\"https://fr.wordpress.org/2020/